202	  \begin{enumerate}
203	    \item \lstinline{[HModule'_toBiprod, HModule'_fromBiprod]}: unfold the two iter-017 LES building blocks to expose the \lstinline{biprod.lift} / \lstinline{biprod.desc} shape.
204	    \item \lstinline{[biprod.lift_desc]}: apply the biproduct universal property
